metadata.name: Kitten Constellations: A Van Gogh-inspired Oil Painting
metadata.description: Get lost in the mesmerizing patterns of the night sky with 'Kitten Constellations'. This NFT artwork blends the playful energy of two fluffy kittens with the captivating beauty of Vincent van Gogh's iconic 'Starry Night'. Created using oil painting techniques, the piece captures the swirling celestial movements of the stars above and the curious antics of the kittens below. A perfect addition to any digital art collection.
